These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
6 different games are played: backgammon, go, bridge, canasta, mah-jongg, billiard
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, ship, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi, tram
1. the person driving the scooter is the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing canasta is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the taxi##2
5. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
8. the person playing billiard is the person driving the skateboard##1
9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| Game         | mah-jongg     | bridge | backgammon | canasta | billiard      | go |
| Transport   | snowmobile | taxi  | scooter    | tram | skateboard | ship    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, horror, mystery, satire, scientific, time-travel
The people have 6 different hobbies: gardening, chess, filmmaking, cooking, woodworking, video-games
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | satire  | scientific | horror   | time-travel | mystery |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | woodworking | chess    | video-games | gardening   | cooking   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-3::.
City: nizza, hamburg, boston, paris, san-francisco, edinburgh
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, golf, handball, ice-hockey, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
4. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's sport is handball is the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |    3    |       4       |     5      |    6     |
| City   | nizza    | san-francisco | boston     | hamburg         | paris       | edinburgh     |
| Sport         | basketball | golf  | cycling | weightlifting | ice-hockey | handball |

