.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, drama, family, satire, scientific, superhero
City: edinburgh, boston, rome, berlin, new-york, venice
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
3. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to rome is the person watching family movies##1
6. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
7. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
9. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | drama     | family     | satire | scientific | superhero |
| City     | venice    | boston | rome | berlin  | new-york       | edinburgh      |

