.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-5::.
6 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog, rabbit, bird, mouse, fish
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, skateboard, snowmobile, train
 1. the person driving the skateboard is between the owner of the rabbit and the person driving the helicopter##2
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the train##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 7. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 8. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
11. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
12. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |     5      |    6    |
| Pet   | mouse | bird | snake | fish    | rabbit    | hedgehog |
| Transport     | car         | bike       | helicopter  | skateboard | snowmobile | train   |

