.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-6::.
6 different pets are kept: mouse, snake, pony, horse, hamster, fish
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, british, polish, russian, spanish, turkish
 1. the british is the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the turkish is on the left of the polish##1
 3. the argentine is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the owner of the horse is the russian##1
 9. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
10. the turkish is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6    |
| Pet   | pony   | hamster   | horse    | fish    | snake  | mouse   |
| Nationality   | turkish | polish | russian | argentine | spanish | british |

