.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-7::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  analyst, engineer, nurse, project-manager, software-developer, writer
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, fanta, juice, mirinda, tea
 1. the person drinking tea is the writer##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
 3. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the writer##3
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the writer##1
 6. the software-developer is on the right of the engineer##1
 7. the engineer is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the nurse is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 9. the analyst is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2       |         3          |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Job     | project-manager | engineer     | software-developer | analyst  | nurse     | writer |
| Beverage   | almond-milk         | mirinda | juice              | fanta | cola | tea |

