.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-9::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: azalea, begonia, poppy, orchid, tulip, iris
1. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person who growsbegonia is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsiris is between the person drinking cola and the person who growspoppy##2
6. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4       |   5    |     6     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola       | 7up     | iced-tea     | fanta  | coffee    |
| Flower      | orchid | azalea | iris | poppy | begonia | tulip |

