 3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the person who growsdahlia is the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 9. the person who growszinnia is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
11. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |       3       |   4   |     5     |    6    |
| Flower    | zinnia | poppy | daisy | dahlia | azalea      | aconite    |
