 1. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
 2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the cain-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
 6. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is the dunhill-smoker##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
11. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |    5    |     6     |
| Cigar   | cain    | old-henry     | dunhill    | fonseca      | tiparillo     | ritmeester      |
