 3. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is the person playing chess##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person playing chess##1
11. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |  3   |       4       |   5   |    6     |
| Beverage      | coffee | mirinda   | milk | hot-chocolate | 7up   | soy-milk |
| Game   | chess    | monopoly | snooker | domino       | scrabble | backgammon     |

