.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-20::.
There are 6 different nationalities: malaysian, dutch, american, nigerian, canadian, polish
The people have 6 different jobs:  doctor, firefighter, freelancer, lawyer, paramedic, security-guard
 1. the lawyer is on the left or right of the polish##3
 2. the canadian is in an even position##4
 3. the nigerian is on the left of the canadian##1
 4. the dutch is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
 5. the security-guard is on the right of the lawyer##1
 6. the malaysian is the paramedic##1
 7. the american is in an even position##4
 8. the freelancer is on the far right##1
 9. the doctor is between the canadian and the firefighter##2
10. the canadian is on the left of the polish##1
11. the dutch is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
12. the lawyer is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |   3    |   4    |       5        |     6      |
| Nationality   | malaysian    | american      | nigerian  | canadian  | polish           | dutch  |
| Job    | paramedic | firefighter | doctor | lawyer | security-guard | freelancer |

 